{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"a totem pole (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that one of the original carvers of <b><a href=\"/wiki/Canadian_totem\" title=\"Canadian totem\">a totem pole</a></b> <i>(detail pictured)</i> described efforts to restore it as akin to \"sending a carpenter to repaint the Mona Lisa\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canadian_totem","retrieved":1782032897087},{"title":"Jean Varraud (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Jean_Varraud\" title=\"Jean Varraud\">Jean Varraud</a></b> once put football star <a href=\"/wiki/Zinedine_Zidane\" title=\"Zinedine Zidane\">Zinedine Zidane</a> on cleaning duty?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Varraud","retrieved":1782032897096},{"title":"1974 Dunedin earthquake (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the number of damage claims lodged after the <b><a href=\"/wiki/1974_Dunedin_earthquake\" title=\"1974 Dunedin earthquake\">1974 Dunedin earthquake</a></b> was unusually high for an earthquake of its magnitude?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1974_Dunedin_earthquake","retrieved":1782032897096},{"title":"Richard M. Hotaling (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Richard_M._Hotaling\" title=\"Richard M. Hotaling\">Richard M. Hotaling</a></b> maintained a herd of <a href=\"/wiki/Holstein_Friesian\" title=\"Holstein Friesian\">Holstein cattle</a> from Holland at his house in California?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_M._Hotaling","retrieved":1782032897096},{"title":"Girl Like Me (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the music video for the <a href=\"/wiki/PinkPantheress\" title=\"PinkPantheress\">PinkPantheress</a> song \"<b><a href=\"/wiki/Girl_Like_Me_(PinkPantheress_song)\" title=\"Girl Like Me (PinkPantheress song)\">Girl Like Me</a></b>\" evokes a \"pre-Brexit utopia\", according to the <i><a href=\"/wiki/New_Statesman\" title=\"New Statesman\">New Statesman</a></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Girl_Like_Me_(PinkPantheress_song)","retrieved":1782032897097},{"title":"a history of New York City (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Greater_Gotham\" title=\"Greater Gotham\">a history of New York City</a></b> examines its subject from the metaphorical viewpoints of a satellite, a jet airliner, a helicopter, a bird, and ground level?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greater_Gotham","retrieved":1782032897098},{"title":"Muhadi Suyono (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Indonesian politician <b><a href=\"/wiki/Muhadi_Suyono\" title=\"Muhadi Suyono\">Muhadi Suyono</a></b> threatened legal action after a Malaysian government website listed <i><a href=\"/wiki/Reog\" title=\"Reog\">reog</a></i> as a Malaysian cultural tradition?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muhadi_Suyono","retrieved":1782032897099},{"title":"Eiga.com (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Eiga.com\" title=\"Eiga.com\">Eiga.com</a></b> withdrew an April Fool's Day prank mocking Donald Trump?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eiga.com","retrieved":1782032897101},{"title":"Kris Lindahl (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Kris_Lindahl\" title=\"Kris Lindahl\">Kris Lindahl</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> billboards have been reacted to with anger, annoyance, and fandom?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kris_Lindahl","retrieved":1782032897102},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<span class=\"mw-empty-elt\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwIQ\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;left&quot;},&qu